text: Central New York Playhouse is a community theater company in DeWitt, New York. Founded in 2012, the Playhouse performs a monthly production in ShoppingTown Mall.https://cnyplayhouse.org/about/history/http://blog.syracuse.com/entertainment/2012/09/new_theater_company_central_ne.html ==References== Category:Theatre companies in New York (state) Category:DeWitt, New York
